<subSubSection pageId="110" pageNumber="506" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="110.[1437,2645,1317,2371]" pageId="110" pageNumber="506">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1437,1673,1983,2016]" pageId="110" pageNumber="506">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Pale Gray White-toothed Shrew is terrestrial and probably nocturnal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
